# Email Template Rules

- Edit `template.hbs` (source) and `data.json` (content), never edit `template.mjml` (auto-generated)
- Put maximum styles inline on MJML elements (color, font-size, font-weight, etc.)
- Use `<mj-style>` only for @font-face, gradients, box-shadow, and media queries
- All comments must be in English
